description:
This is a 36 minute workout called 'Guided Meditation - Raising your vibration with the Angels' from the channel Natasha Tome.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Deep Recharge and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This video is a guided meditation that raises your vibration to the fifth dimension, which leads you on the ascension pathway. You will be connected to ten Archangels, who will help you open and activate your 12 chakras. This will bring you confidence, hope, wisdom and love....
